---
import Header from '../components/Header.astro'
import LeftInfo from '../components/LeftInfo.astro'
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="Welcome to Astro!">
  <Header />
  <LeftInfo />
  <main class="max-w-[1000px] mx-auto px-10 flex flex-col gap-10">
    <section class="min-h-[calc(100vh-120px)] flex items-center justify-center relative">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 -translate-y-[50px]">
        <h2 class="text-secondary">Hi, mi name is</h2>
        <h1 class="text-7xl font-bold text-white/90">Franco Perez.</h1>
        <h2 class="text-7xl font-bold text-white/70">I'm a Full Stack Developer</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-white/70 text-pretty w-1/2 my-4">I am a passionate Full Stack Developer with a strong focus on creating dynamic and responsive web applications. I have experience in both front-end and back-end development, and I am always eager to learn new technologies and improve my skills.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section id="about" class="min-h-[calc(100vh-120px)]">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white/90"><span class="text-secondary mr-2">01.</span> About Me</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/70 text-pretty">I am a Full Stack Developer with a passion for creating dynamic and responsive web applications. I have experience in both front-end and back-end development, and I am always eager to learn new technologies and improve my skills.</p>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/70 text-pretty">I have a strong background in HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, and I am proficient in frameworks such as React, Angular, and Vue.js. On the back-end, I have experience with Node.js, Express, and MongoDB.</p>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/70 text-pretty">I am a quick learner and a team player, and I enjoy collaborating with others to create innovative solutions. I am always looking for new challenges and opportunities to grow as a developer.</p>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/70 text-pretty">In my free time, I enjoy working on personal projects, contributing to open source, and staying up to date with the latest trends in web development.</p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
